title: Wacky Delly
description: Adventures of Sal Ami, Betty Bologna, and Mr. Cheese at the Wacky Delly where chaos reigns.
quote: I am the cheese. I am the best character on the show. I am better than both the salami and the bologna combined.
altHero: a happy bologna with hair and bow in a crudely drawn deli
alt1: a crudely drawn store with sign “Wacky Delly”
alt2: a grumpy salami and wedge of cheese
alt3: a meatloaf type dish garnished with pineapple on a picnic table
alt4: the cheese screams in front of the bologna
